Bussiness analyst typically moves in between the business and the developers.
If the developers have a question, they have to go back to the customer and find the answer.

Product Owner should have most of the answers. If the developer has a question, they shouldn't have email someone for answer.
They own the product and have the authority to make real time decission.

A Product Manager is closer to Product owner.

Project mananger works on long term startegy for a product, They Create a budget, looks at competing Products.

Product owner must be commited with the team.
So if the developer has some question, he should ask the product owner.